<h3>About Us</h3>

<h4>Overview</h4>British Airways Virtual is one of the best virtual airlines out there. We have over 2000 real world British Airways routes and are constantly trying to be the best. We have been using several flight trackers over the years including: FSAirlines, VAFS and now phpVMS. We were always dominating the leaderboard of FSAirlines and were always in the top 50 on VAFS and now we have decided that we will thrive even more using phpVMS.<br><br> As a Virtual Airline, we have been going since September of 2012. We orrigionally started as an airline called FlyAirUK which has built up a very good reputation. We have intergrated this into British Airways Virtual as our training department.  

