<h4>Our Goals</h4>
Our goal is to provide the most realistic and enjoyable experiance that is possible in the flight simulator world to all of our pilots through our staff team and services. We are striving to become one of the best virtual airlines in the world. Aiming to be the virtual airline that everyone is talking about in the virtual airline community. Our latest goal is migrating to a new flight tracking software and a complete new website, and grow to a bigger better future. 

